            "id": 6408174,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 費城半導體大漲1.06%，報7916.11點",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間06日09:30，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>上漲82.72點（或1.06%），暫報7916.11點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+5.04%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.15%</li><li>近 3 月：+5.2%</li><li>近 6 月：+18.98%</li><li>今年以來：+10.59%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以和康電訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MTSI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MTSI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MTSI-US</a>)領漲。和康電訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MTSI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MTSI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MTSI-US</a>)上漲3.9%；思佳訊半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SWKS:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SWKS\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SWKS-US</a>)上漲3.7%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)上漲2.48%；連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)上漲1.8%；美光科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:MU:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/MU\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">MU-US</a>)上漲1.72%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>部分成分股表現相對疲軟，安謀控股公司(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ARM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ARM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ARM-US</a>)下跌3.84%；艾司摩爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ASML:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ASML\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ASML-US</a>)下跌3.13%；應用材料(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMAT:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMAT\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMAT-US</a>)下跌1.51%；泰瑞達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TER:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TER\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TER-US</a>)下跌0.83%；亞德諾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADI-US</a>)下跌0.7%。</p></section></main>",
